{{Infobox company | | name = Another World Entertainment | logo = Another world entertainment logo.jpg | logo_size = 220px | type = | foundation = January 2006 | location = [[Copenhagen, Denmark]] | key_people = | industry = [[Home video]] | products = [[DVD]], [[Blu-ray Disc]] | homepage = [http://www.anotherworldent.com Official site] }} '''Another World Entertainment''' (also known as simply '''AWE''') is a Danish home video distribution company.
Another World Entertainment was established in January 2006 and has been a leading distributor of a number of titles on [[DVD]] and more recently, [[Blu-ray Disc]]. Horror films are the company's most released genre, having released several [[cannibal film|cannibal]], [[zombie film|zombie]] and [[vampire film|vampire]] films. However, other genres do include drama, comedy, sci-fi, thriller, action and western.
