'''Radio Television Elmag''' is a broadcasting [[company]] based in [[Podgorica]], [[Montenegro]]. RTV Elmag consists of TV Elmag and Radio Elmag.

Radio Elmag was the first private [[FM broadcasting|FM]] radio station in Montenegro and is receivable throughout the country. Its transmission frequency in [[Podgorica]] is 96.00 FM.

The owner is Gojko Mitrovic. Radio Elmag won many rewards and is considered as the best in Montenegro.
